    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>#Mac安装Node</p><h2 id="安装HomeBrew"><a href="#安装HomeBrew" class="headerlink" title="安装HomeBrew"></a>安装HomeBrew</h2><p>卸载brew</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">ruby -e &quot;$(curl -fsSL https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Homebrew/install/master/uninstall)&quot;</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>安装brew</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">ruby -e &quot;$(curl -fsSL https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Homebrew/install/master/install)&quot;</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="HomeBrew安装Node-js"><a href="#HomeBrew安装Node-js" class="headerlink" title="HomeBrew安装Node.js"></a>HomeBrew安装Node.js</h2><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">brew install node</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="Node管理版本工具n"><a href="#Node管理版本工具n" class="headerlink" title="Node管理版本工具n"></a>Node管理版本工具n</h2><p>全局安装n</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">npm intall -g n</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>切换淘宝源</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">npm config set registry http://registry.npm.taobao.org/</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>用n安装node最新版本</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">sudo n stable</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>终端输入n可以切换node版本</p><h2 id="安装淘宝npm镜像"><a href="#安装淘宝npm镜像" class="headerlink" title="安装淘宝npm镜像"></a>安装淘宝npm镜像</h2><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr